content:
What information should be included in the customer agreement document? 
As for generating the document, here's a sample JavaScript code that can create a new text file in the user's local system:
function download(text, name, type) {
  var a = document.createElement("a");
  var file = new Blob([text], {type: type});
  a.href = URL.createObjectURL(file);
  a.download = name;
  a.click();
}
download("Sample text", "customer_agreement.txt", "text/plain");

What other features do you want to add to the document generator?
